      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a small door ding on the passenger side, and some fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the floor mats. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it will likely need new tires and a brake pad replacement in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone looking for dependable transportation without the premium price tag.",
