      "description": "Looking for a fantastic project with heaps of potential? This vehicle is the perfect canvas for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast! While it's in rougher shape and definitely needs some TLC and mechanical repairs to get back on the road, it\u2019s priced to move and offers a great opportunity to own a car at a bargain. If you've got the tools and the passion, this could be your next rewarding weekend project!",
