      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive care, presenting in showroom-fresh condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, matched by pristine alloy wheels and original trim. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the high-grade leather upholstery retains its original scent and supple texture, completely free from wear or creasing. Every electronic component and convenience feature functions flawlessly, exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is peerless, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified specialists. Always garaged under a silk cover and never exposed to inclement weather, this is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously preserved masterpiece that delivers a driving experience indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
